{
  "stem": "12150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they reported on their fellow Jews, which is not very nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got off the bus, I remember, we had a big lake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was walking alongside the lake, instead of the main street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I crossed through a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed home one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I may have gotten back at night, the last bus, so nobody-- in [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ungvar, ?] I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had papers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody knew me, exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Munkats, ?] I was afraid of fellow Jews, that would recognize me, and report me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They get a few dollars, a few-- not dollars, but-- and those people were tortured.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they reported somebody who had forged papers, these people were tortured, and then thrown into labor camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was the situation, until 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in 1944, of course, every city-- Elizabeth said a different date.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "According to my-- my records, it was in April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In April, 1944-- probably the beginning of April, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Germans occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And since this was a part of Hungary, it was occupied by Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now their systematic-- and apparently it wasn't the first time that they did this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Within two weeks-- or first, they-- one week, they didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got acquainted with the circumstances, or the area, the leaders of the SS, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after a week, they posted-- posted notices all over that all the Jewish people from this and this city-- they divided the town by areas, and listed all the streets that have to report here, and here, and here-- this and this date.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they can carry one suitcase away, and so much, and so much-- all the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
